reviews.review_text: HOOOOOONK ! I Agree. Not About Donna But Mr. Clemmons. Yep. Though He Had His Band. I Find It Funny How He Fit In With Springhead. Actually I Feel The Same Way About "Spruce" Honk, Honk, Hooooooonk ! Back To The Jersey $wamp$ You Devil !  On The Other Hand. I Think Charlie Miller Is Actually An Alchemist. He's Figured Out How To Turn Petroleum Tape Into Gold ! Thank You Master Miller. I'm Still Reeling From These Warfields. Thank You !!!
